# EntryThoughtSheet — shell layout (STRICT)

The **gap under the sheet** bug returns whenever the modal shell deviates from this pattern. Do not "fix" keyboard or animation issues by changing the shell.

## Required structure

```
Modal (transparent, overFullScreen)
└── GestureHandlerRootView { flex: 1 }          // RNGH in Modal needs this on iOS
    └── View { flex: 1, backgroundColor: scrim } // testID: entry-read-sheet
        ├── Pressable { flex: 1 }                // dismiss backdrop
        └── View { sheet styles }                // testID: entry-thought-sheet — LAST child
            └── content (PanGestureHandler on grabber strip only, ScrollView / TextInput)
```

Sheet is pinned to the **bottom by flex column** (dismiss grows, sheet is last sibling). Content-sized height + `paddingBottom: max(safeArea, spacing)`.

## Forbidden on the sheet shell (causes gap or float)

- `KeyboardAvoidingView` wrapping the sheet (leaves bottom padding / lifts sheet at rest)
- `position: 'absolute'`, `bottom: 0`, `justifyContent: 'flex-end'` on modal root
- `translateY` / `Animated.View` motion wrapper on the sheet container
- `StyleSheet.absoluteFillObject` instead of `flex: 1` on modal root
- Nested `GestureHandlerRootView` beyond the single root inside Modal
- `Dimensions.get('screen')` fixed height on modal root

## Allowed

- `maxHeight: '88%'` (compact) or numeric cap (expanded) on the **sheet View**
- `KeyboardAvoidingView` only inside CaptureScreen — **never** inside this Modal
- Keyboard inset: adjust **inner** editor `paddingBottom` via `keyboardWillShow` listeners — not the shell
- Pan gestures: detection only on grabber strip; no drag translation on shell

## Keyboard / edit mode

- TextInput lives **inside** sheet, **outside** ScrollView when expanded
- Never call `Keyboard.dismiss()` on sheet open or during typing
- **Save on dismiss/collapse only** — no debounced autosave while typing (avoids parent re-renders and sync churn)
- `onEntryUpdated`: update stream lists only — do **not** replace `readEntry` while sheet is open

## Reference

Working baseline: git `6ee28ba` `EntryReadSheet.tsx` shell (flex dismiss + plain sheet child).  
Guard test: `components/__tests__/EntryReadSheet.test.tsx` — "pins sheet with flex column shell".
